Finance Lawyer 1-3 PQE, Dubai
Finance Lawyer 1-3 PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This is a fantastic opportunity for a banking lawyer to join the international banking department of this heavyweight US law firm in their Dubai office.
Ideal candidates will have high quality generalist banking/finance experience gained from a recognised finance practice, ideally in the region.
Islamic finance experience is highly desirablealthough the candidate will be expected to do all forms of banking.
Should you wish to apply for this role, please contact Richard McLerie (richard@jlegal.com) for a confidential chat.
